{"tid":1617502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「唔好再被轉風向系列」熱門ＴＯＰ１０有４個講緊謝振中條撚樣","createTime":"2019-10-03T22:33:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T03:35:59.000Z","uid":156582,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2f4771fd5ed18c2bb8cd36e1727b9b60bcb02ac9","tid":1617502,"uid":156582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T22:33:15.000Z","msg":"狙擊隻黑警還狙擊，大家請睇清睇楚我地而家面對緊咩危機<br />\n<br />\n係緊急法呀！！<br />\n<br />\n緊急法一有先例，以後特區政府就可以無視立法會為所欲為<br />\n辱警、國教、23條、送中條例等等日後唔需要怕任何爭議<br />\n而且緊急法仲包括左任意拘捕任何人、斷網、任意沒收財產等等<br />\n<br />\n因此緊急法本身已經係一項極危險嘅事！<br />\n<br />\n唔好再諗禁蒙面法立左之後要點，唔好浪費太多精神去理一隻狗<br />\n集中火力做文宣，而家只有一樣野要做，就係發起<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全港反緊急法！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">緊急法＝獨裁政府任意妄為</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"23d5a9ae784975f1c0bbdd35965717d17646d4c9","tid":1617502,"uid":156582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T22:34:33.000Z","msg":"唔可以開先例畀港共為所欲為"},{"pid":"78893d136782b5674df914997aecf13a30ca151e","tid":1617502,"uid":156582,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T22:35:29.000Z","msg":"想攬炒冇問題<br />\n<br />\n但要攬炒都要畀外國知咩事先炒到<br />\n外國唔會好清楚知道緊急法代表緊啲咩<br />\n然後就戇鳩鳩過撚左，成班連登仔係度自HIGH，但人地都唔知咩事<br />\n<br />\n所以一定要加緊文宣，畀外國知道緊急法＝獨裁政府為所欲為"},{"pid":"25705937eb1ce6978ca0440c5f2556b1b4cc283b","tid":1617502,"uid":270856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T22:36:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a06abb8bed6c6c1d2db184da44e9ea4b80b1b889","tid":1617502,"uid":139676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T22:38:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=